cs.DS, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.CY, cs.CL 

The paper deals with the problem of organizing and maintaining a scientist's publications, which involves tasks such as merging, deleting, and correcting titles of papers. This problem is related to data structures (cs.DS) and information retrieval (cs.IR), as well as databases (cs.DB) and cybersecurity (cs.CY) since it involves managing and securing personal information. Additionally, natural language processing (cs.CL) may also be relevant for correcting titles of papers.
